<h2 id="about-the-speaker">About the Speaker</h2>

<h3 id="bio">Bio</h3>
<p>Austin Rochford is the Chief Data Scientist at Kibo Commerce. He is a recovering mathematician and is passionate about math education, Bayesian statistics, and machine learning.</p>

